OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChristmas savings clubs    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmoney to be protected by   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fnew laws                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Savings clubs for shoppers will soon be
OL,6, protected under new laws to be         
OL,7, introduced by the government.          
OL,9,FMany families pay into schemes         
OL,10,Fthroughout the year to spend on        
OL,11,FChristmas, weddings or home projects.  
OL,13,FThese clubs are not yet covered by the 
OL,14,FFinancial Services Compensation Scheme.
OL,16,FBut new laws mean even if the company  
OL,17,Fgoes bust, shoppers' money will still  
OL,18,Fbe protected. It is aimed at preventing
OL,19,Fscandals like the collapse of Christmas
OL,20,Fsavings club Farepak in 2006.          
